{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"fields":{"description":"# S4 — CI service account + credentials (SSM-backed)\n\nPart of epic 1fa8 (CI as a second Gerrit gate vote via gerrit-to-platform → GitHub Actions).\n\n## Why\nThe CI vote-back SSHes into Gerrit as a service account (the g2p production pattern); g2p (running\nin the Gerrit container) also needs a GitHub PAT to `workflow_dispatch`. Both credentials must\nfollow the infra's no-plaintext invariant: SSM SecureString + materialize-at-boot (as with the bot\ntoken, deploy key, OAuth secret).\n\n## What\nProvision the CI Gerrit service account (with the `Verified` ACL), and wire the PAT + SSH key\nthrough SSM and the boot-time fetch, plus the GitHub-side vars/secret. Record the inbound\nGitHub→Gerrit SSH trust path as an ADR.\n\n## Scope\n- `infra/gerrit/service-user.sh` (provision the account, as a template), `infra/terraform/ssm.tf`\n  (new SecureString slots), `infra/scripts/fetch-secrets.sh` (host-side materialization).\n- GitHub repo vars/secret; new ADR for the inbound SSH trust path. Pairs with S3.\n- Out of scope: the workflow (S5), the gate (S1).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Provision the CI Gerrit service account via `infra/gerrit/service-user.sh` (account + group +\n      the `Verified -1..+1` ACL from S1).\n- [ ] Add the g2p PAT — **fine-grained, single-repo (`navapbc/rebar`)**, Actions read/write +\n      Contents/Metadata read (NOT a classic org-wide PAT) — and the service-account SSH key to\n      `infra/terraform/ssm.tf` (`rebar_secret_params`, `ignore_changes=value`); add the PAT leaf to\n      `infra/scripts/fetch-secrets.sh` (it already writes the container `.env` that g2p-in-container\n      reads — no host-side materialization needed).\n- [ ] Set GitHub repo vars `GERRIT_SERVER` / `GERRIT_SSH_USER` / `GERRIT_KNOWN_HOSTS` /\n      `GERRIT_URL` and secret `GERRIT_SSH_PRIVKEY`.\n- [ ] Define a rotation + retire path for both the PAT and `GERRIT_SSH_PRIVKEY` (compromise\n      response + PoC decommission).\n- [ ] Write an ADR recording the inbound GitHub→Gerrit SSH vote path (blast radius, key scope)."}},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"EDIT","timestamp":1782960352422169001,"uuid":"a856708d-aeb3-43b0-ae07-312a10bd9479"}